,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1cb85a2f6fbb4b1a2d0d208b8467c291658a99c9","tid":1392081,"uid":199182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:30:52.000Z","msg":"黎緊暑假決定去旅行，人生第一次坐長途機去歐洲，買左坐特選經濟艙，聽人講個位闊落啲，但想問下各位覺得有冇需要帶頸枕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然個問題好似好無聊，但係去咁遠旅遊又吾想帶太多瑣碎野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:36:43.000Z","msg":"有，PEY唔係flat bed"},{"pid":"465a0e985386c2503e25097cf5f5bd41caa4e7ea","tid":1392081,"uid":16376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:47:49.000Z","msg":"PEY要睇邊個架 A350外既PEY真係坐Y好過"},{"pid":"8ab9fc142a4b38bfe8c7f52bcdecf6d609572c42","tid":1392081,"uid":101698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:42:08.000Z","msg":"777 PEY better than airbus <br />\nService-wise: have amenity kit, welcome drink, and different menu from EY, nth much different"},{"pid":"560b88a80037b129421adc2105b0d99f5dec3461","tid":1392081,"uid":33433,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:51:47.000Z","msg":"買真係不了 econ double價錢<br />\n用AM換 只係比多三分一<br />\n<br />\n搭過A350 PEY 叫做多啲腳位同挨後啲<br />\n應該會瞓好左<br />\n腳長咪坐中間果4個位<br />\n前排椅腳會阻住你伸腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n坐靠窗口腳位無野阻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd12d42a859ad0cbfe60db90ee33807ed410cbd","tid":1392081,"uid":22218,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:01:31.000Z","msg":"頸枕都係需要嘅<br />\n<br />\n坐過去加拿大<br />\n位闊少少，可以挨後多d，leg room多d，耳筒聲靚d，上機有杯野飲，有個amenity kit(連埋老婆同女總共攞咗六個，六個條拉鏈都係爛嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n唔算特別好，係econ真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca6b9bf669c9638b8ff951bcc3137098326a1017","tid":1392081,"uid":80533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:19:49.000Z","msg":"坐過A350 PEY long haul<br />\n好處咪上面講個堆<br />\n位闊少少<br />\nReclining角度大d<br />\nAmenity kit, welcome drink, menu唔同<br />\nA350有腳踏<br />\n<br />\n我自己鍾意坐窗口位<br />\n所以2-4-2 configuration會方便d我出去去廁所<br />\n<br />\n但其實PEY都係坐第一排先好<br />\n我睇住我隔離個男人下下較到角度最大<br />\n佢後面個個又係男人黎<br />\n壓到佢無咩位淨咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋a350廁所同econ共用仲要行好後<br />\n姐係食完飯就落機個d時間有排排<br />\n777有某隻機型係pey獨立一個廁所<br />\n<br />\n頸枕最好有<br />\n始終唔係平訓，護住條頸都舒服d"},{"pid":"7d8dca97fd33df64a12ae6730f7cda367d4e38e9","tid":1392081,"uid":185252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1cb85a2f6fbb4b1a2d0d208b8467c291658a99c9","tid":1392081,"uid":199182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:30:52.000Z","msg":"黎緊暑假決定去旅行，人生第一次坐長途機去歐洲，買左坐特選經濟艙，聽人講個位闊落啲，但想問下各位覺得有冇需要帶頸枕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然個問題好似好無聊，但係去咁遠旅遊又吾想帶太多瑣碎野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:25:22.000Z","msg":"有頸枕會舒服D, 不過我近來都覺得費時帶太多野, 頸枕懶得帶<br />\n<br />\nA350, 尤其係1000好OK, 777就..... 有兩款<br />\n一款係冇得掘托小腿, 果款就真係非常之唔舒適<br />\n<br />\n另外廁所係同ECON共用, 即係ECON人都會行上黎用你個廁所<br />\n<br />\n如果你身形唔係大, 其實好OK的, 同以前既BUSINESS CLASS其實都差不多"},{"pid":"a5b84f9276864daed619bb4b7d3d136d092353fb","tid":1392081,"uid":36758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:28:10.000Z","msg":"坐過pey來回Mel ，夜機<br />\n去嗰程A350 坐中間，兩邊有人都有啲辛苦<br />\n回程777 坐窗口位好好多，而且唔爆，側邊無人好好坐<br />\n廁所都要用番econ嗰個<br />\n夜機瞓教好靜，多少少privacy <br />\n但係上次有強國人econ走上黎坐，俾空姐趕番走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10606c0b89d5486c96bb81eed6d7a26b5e31de4c","tid":1392081,"uid":168010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:06:30.000Z","msg":"睇下咩機型...<br />\nA350-1000真係狗都唔屌<br />\nBA PY 2-4-2 同Y 3-3-3 唔覺